258
00:16:26,875 --> 00:16:29,178
Life is ultimately just a game.

259
00:16:29,178 --> 00:16:32,147
Whoever enjoys herself the most
before the game's over wins.

260
00:16:41,990 --> 00:16:43,692
Don't let her get away!

261
00:16:43,692 --> 00:16:44,793
Darn it!

262
00:16:44,793 --> 00:16:48,230
It's because of contingencies like this
that I wanted to use Hell Girl!

263
00:16:48,230 --> 00:16:51,131
Men are so useless
when you need them most!

264
00:17:04,379 --> 00:17:06,248
Midnight!

