274
00:17:33,675 --> 00:17:36,078
I am Ai Enma.

275
00:17:36,078 --> 00:17:38,847
Hell Girl?!

276
00:17:38,847 --> 00:17:41,350
Take it.

277
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:45,187
If you really want retribution,

278
00:17:45,187 --> 00:17:47,756
untie this red thread.

279
00:17:47,756 --> 00:17:53,161
By untying the thread, you will
enter into a covenant with me.

280
00:17:53,161 --> 00:17:57,427
The object of your vengeance will
immediately be banished to Hell.

281
00:17:59,234 --> 00:18:00,636
Right away?!

282
00:18:00,636 --> 00:18:02,738
Not decades from now?!

283
00:18:02,738 --> 00:18:04,006
Yes.

284
00:18:04,006 --> 00:18:05,307
However,

285
00:18:05,307 --> 00:18:06,842
once you have your retribution,

286
00:18:06,842 --> 00:18:10,078
you will have to pay
the price for it as well.

287
00:18:10,078 --> 00:18:12,981
Curses come home to roost.

288
00:18:12,981 --> 00:18:16,551
After you die, your soul will go to Hell.

289
00:18:16,551 --> 00:18:18,520
This world is Hell!

290
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:20,317
As long as that woman is alive!

291
00:18:22,257 --> 00:18:25,249
Your grievance has been heard.

292
00:18:31,233 --> 00:18:32,530
Did you take care of her?!

293
00:18:36,405 --> 00:18:37,895
