294
00:18:46,682 --> 00:18:47,449
This is!

295
00:18:47,449 --> 00:18:47,916
"Dead Line Incorporated"
This is!

296
00:18:47,916 --> 00:18:49,406
"Dead Line Incorporated"

297
00:18:51,486 --> 00:18:54,546
Oh, right. I...

