let you people...mess up my life!

303
00:19:39,267 --> 00:19:41,536
I've found my resolve, thanks to you!

304
00:19:41,536 --> 00:19:43,505
No matter what methods I have to use,

305
00:19:43,505 --> 00:19:45,841
I'll win the game of life!

306
00:19:45,841 --> 00:19:48,877
Even if I have to sacrifice
every person out there!

307
00:19:48,877 --> 00:19:51,480
You'll be the first.

308
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:54,142
You'll be the first to be sacrificed.

309
00:19:58,620 --> 00:20:00,383
You're next.

