314
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:12,033
"Dead Line Incorporated"
What?!

315
00:20:12,033 --> 00:20:13,034
What?!

316
00:20:13,034 --> 00:20:15,400
I told you it's your turn, didn't I?

317
00:20:25,347 --> 00:20:28,250
O pitiful shadow lost in the darkness...

318
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:30,752
Demeaning and bringing harm to others...

319
00:20:30,752 --> 00:20:33,482
A damned soul, wallowing in sin...

320
00:20:35,090 --> 00:20:37,581
Care to give death a try?

321
00:20:50,038 --> 00:20:51,440
Why?!

322
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:55,444
Why do I have to be killed
over and over again?!

323
00:20:55,444 --> 00:20:57,078
Not over and over.

324
00:20:57,078 --> 00:20:57,976
What?

325
00:20:59,381 --> 00:21:00,814
For eternity.

326
00:21:04,252 --> 00:21:09,019
I consign this grievance to Hell...

327
00:21:18,166 --> 00:21:19,768
