living in Ms. Riho's condo, but...

336
00:21:45,660 --> 00:21:47,262
Who are you talking to?

337
00:21:47,262 --> 00:21:48,663
Huh?

338
00:21:48,663 --> 00:21:50,932
Uh, who was I talking to?

339
00:21:50,932 --> 00:21:54,069
