343
00:22:05,313 --> 00:22:07,338
Lost in the darkness...

344
00:22:16,291 --> 00:22:17,986
Wow!

345
00:22:28,303 --> 00:22:32,007
When I die, I'm going
to Hell without fail.

346
00:22:32,007 --> 00:22:34,709
We're talking decades until that happens.

347
00:22:34,709 --> 00:22:37,012
Life is ultimately just a game.

348
00:22:37,012 --> 00:22:41,216
Whoever enjoys herself the most
before the game's over wins.

349
00:22:41,216 --> 00:22:44,653
Yeah, that's true.

350
00:22:44,653 --> 00:22:48,453
I'm going to enjoy this game
to my heart's content.

